the words above.

10
00:00:54,333 --> 00:00:54,694
"'Hist!

11
00:00:55,054 --> 00:00:56,737
Did you hear that noise, Capico?

12
00:00:57,218 --> 00:00:58,880
Take the bucket, will ye, Archie?

13
00:00:59,201 --> 00:01:00,563
What noise d'ye mean?'

14
00:01:00,743 --> 00:01:02,666
"'There it is again under the hatches.

